673
00:35:24,166 --> 00:35:24,746
Caffettino?

674
00:35:25,206 --> 00:35:25,626
Zabaglione.

675
00:35:26,673 --> 00:35:27,454
Questo all'ancolo.

676
00:35:27,793 --> 00:35:28,295
