754
00:38:41,106 --> 00:38:46,608
Eh beh, ma sai... Ciao Sara.

755
00:38:47,110 --> 00:38:47,230
Ciao.

756
00:38:47,250 --> 00:38:47,429
Ciao.

757
00:38:50,396 --> 00:38:50,896
Ciao Sara.

758
00:38:53,177 --> 00:38:53,998
Ciao.

759
00:38:54,018 --> 00:38:55,818
Ciao.

760
00:38:56,139 --> 00:39:01,041
